exceed—","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(i) $1,000 per month for officers performing qualifying flying duty relating to remotely piloted aircraft (RPA); or","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(ii) $850 per month for officers performing other qualifying flying duty; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(B) an aviation bonus under subsection (b) may not exceed, for each 12-month period of obligated service agreed to under subsection (d)—","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(i) $35,000 for officers performing qualifying flying duty relating to remotely piloted aircraft; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(ii) $25,000 for officers performing other qualifying flying duty.”","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(2) to (4). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/328/s616/b"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–328, § 616(b)","children":[],"tail":", added par. (2) and redesignated former pars. (2) and (3) as (3) and (4), respectively."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (i). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/328/s614/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–328, § 614(4)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “"},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2017-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 2017","children":[],"tail":"” for “"},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2016-12-31"},"text":"December 31, 2016","children":[],"tail":"”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2015—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/92/s617/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–92, § 617(a)","children":[],"tail":", designated existing provisions as par. (1) and inserted heading, redesignated former pars. (1) to (5) as subpars. (A) to (E), respectively, of par. (1) and realigned margins, and added par. (2)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(1)(A). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"